HACIFusion-BEV

This repository is a research extension based on BEVFusion:
"BEVFusion: A Simple and Robust LiDAR-Camera Fusion Framework"
by Tingting Liang, Hongwei Xie, Kaicheng Yu, Zhongyu Xia,
Zhiwei Lin, Yongtao Wang, Tao Tang, Bing Wang and Zhi Tang.

The repository preserves the original BEVFusion/OpenMMLab-style
code structure and license notice, and adds research modifications
for LiDAR-Camera BEV fusion, especially the hybrid attention and
convolutional induction fusion module implemented mainly in:

  mmdet3d/models/detectors/bevf_faster_rcnn_aug.py

Additional exploratory research code from the master's project is
kept separately under:

  research_extras/

The main research contribution corresponds to:

"Hybrid Attention and Convolutional Induction Network for
LiDAR-Camera BEV Fusion in Complex Road Scenes"
DOI: https://doi.org/10.1049/itr2.70273

